Class AbstractRdkitMatchedPairsMultipleCutsNodeModel

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RdkitMatchedPairsNodeModel, RdkitMMPFragmentNodeModel

    public abstract class AbstractRdkitMatchedPairsMultipleCutsNodeModel
extends org.knime.core.node.NodeModel
    Abstract class for the shared code for the MMP and Molecule fragment nodes. Provides methods to retrieve the molecule from the input cell as an ROMol object, and handles column selection via the configure(DataTableSpec[]) implementation. Subclasses must intialise the m_Logger.
    Author:
    "Stephen Roughley "
